core":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6f07dc618d21a98b31c33dc1f5cad98f8d3a538","tid":1827372,"uid":260991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"年年都會星到十送一先跌返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"唔送就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔送就走人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"其實睇佢cash flow就算0增長都可以再頂一兩年十送一"},{"pid":"42c0471d704f5bf32d73160505fd304a2b1a8484","tid":1827372,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32305b496b8b0d77024cafba9dd98af8f9d988b6","tid":1827372,"uid":104645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"連3仔個名都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:41:37.000Z","msg":"無錯到<br />\n要用電來製煤"},{"pid":"4e59f51c46bcd3b183550ca304ce09dd11fb396e","tid":1827372,"uid":68728,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"2018年唔計物業重估 煤氣賺得72億<br />\n但派息己經要派54億 （派息比率75%）<br />\n<br />\n而2018做左十送一 即係係每股派息不變下 2019年要派多10% 派59億<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得佢2019上半年己經有倒退<br />\n而家個情況己經唔健康 佢派息個數字真係唔洗幾年就追到盈利<br />\n<br />\n到時一係減派息 一係唔做十送一&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n派息金額59億 姐係做多2次十送一個派息金額就會變成72億 己經追到個盈利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9f723e165f250fb515d6a06d5555cabf8db930","tid":1827372,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"冇人用啦"},{"pid":"b54147f10fb4d9d2e81524d13b14b9b5023e8264","tid":1827372,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2365000/2368013/88779_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2365000%2F2368013%2F88779_600.png&h=00a87de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imoney.hket.com/article/2368013?fbclid=IwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimoney.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2368013%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=e2d4198c\" target=\"_blank\">http://imoney.hket.com/article/2368013?fbclid=IwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">陳永堅</span>也指香港方面，現在<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人用煤氣已愈來愈少</span>，「以前一戶有3人，現在一戶只有2.5個人，人口少了，每個家庭簡單了，在家煮食要求又低了，洗澡會在家吃飯未必，好多人出街食，尤其住在納米樓的，<span style=\"color: red;\">基本上沒有廚房</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n他也坦言，<span style=\"color: red;\">煤氣跟電力的競爭很大</span>，「一條煤氣喉來到你家，入到廚房，是否代表你煮食會全用到煤氣？實際上並不如此，如你煲飯會用電飯煲，我相信有99%的香港人也用電飯煲煲飯，你煲湯很多時用電子瓦罉、壓力煲等，你早餐吃的多士也是用多士爐製作，也是用電的；以往用水煲煲水，現在大家也普遍改用電水煲，70年代後也出現了微波爐，其後也有電磁爐的出現，<span style=\"color: red;\">因此電力取了我們很多的市場</span>，電力跟我們有很大競爭。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲連登仔覺得自己醒過煤氣管理層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0005816742045a5a9379aab703ef13a37e819524","tid":1827372,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e662db10b1a66429ea781ee6174d0fa05afffe83","tid":1827372,"uid":241006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"入咗啲0006<br />\n想試下煤氣<br />\n有冇話咩價位入比較好<br />\n利申 低風險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:49:30.000Z","msg":"14.98"},{"pid":"cca34f036a433f4a640c79f0371bdb8a4bf0314b","tid":1827372,"uid":68728,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"1. 估值PE過高 接近30 其他公用股只係15<br />\n2. 盈利負增長 2019全年業績必定更差<br />\n3. 煤氣係夕陽行業 未來將被電全部取代<br />\n4. 煤氣加價能力低 10年只加得7次價 而且每次增幅少<br />\n5. 四叔已退休 接班人能力成疑<br />\n6. 本地市場己飽和 中國市場競爭大<br />\n7. 息率奇低 不夠2厘<br />\n8. 十送一只係財技 派完每股股權會被攤薄 最後得個吉"},{"pid":"b544a27b056b6ff32bbad4c8c55cd245a94bf031","tid":1827372,"uid":61994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:18:53.000Z","msg":"即係hold到4月左右好走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54a7c40db4a2771ac2c5f667f66b8c87bff7ed4","tid":1827372,"uid":68728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"十送一紅股叫得響亮，十拆十一股卻難勾起興趣，送紅股後股數雖然增多，但在總盈利不變下，每股盈利按比例攤薄，一來一回投資價值不會有大變化，即使說股數多了，流通量增加了，利好股價，但亦不能成為持續推升股價的理由，否則一步到位，一次過一送一股，股價豈非多升九倍？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解咁多傻散以為十送一真係有著數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b131cef4183fc0c9ad249db366d826af37757f41","tid":1827372,"uid":68728,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"煤氣20年加得7次價 每次仲要加少過5% 通脹都追唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為3仔有壟斷地位 冇法例利潤管制 就可以加價<br />\n但事實上係 佢一加得多價 就會推人去用電 所以加價能力好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2380000/2382398/LB_01_600.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"092afaa53db82702c2d3ee647a9dc41e330c919b","tid":1827372,"uid":68728,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"隔離post巴打前年屋企裝修，全屋轉哂做用電<br />\n放棄咗用煤氣，拆咗煤氣熱水爐，買咗 IZU 呢款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9EPNOP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EPNOP0.jpg&h=d0f70b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冬天最少可以沖20分鐘都仲有熱水唔<br />\n電器同科技只會愈來愈進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71af4fc38d6348f11dd5bd6450ac78e822c82dfb","tid":1827372,"uid":61994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re